item.title: CVE-2010-3048|2024-08-07T02:55:46.696Z -- cisco -- unified%20personal%20communicator
item.description: Cisco Unified Personal Communicator 7.0 (1.13056) does not free allocated memory for received data and does not perform validation if memory allocation is successful, causing a remote denial of service condition.
